<br>
Of course this may all be just a rumor...<br>
<br>
Oh, and I happen to know for a fact that she enjoys sacrificing souls to Innoruuk if anyone feels burdened by advanced seasons.  She can gleefully return anyone to a spry level 52 if it is their desire.<br>
